### 1. 测试 hello 接口
GET http://localhost:8081/hello

### 2. 测试 about 接口
GET http://localhost:8081/about

### 3. 查询所有用户
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/all

### 4. 根据ID查询用户
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/id/1

### 5. 查询所有学生
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/role/student

### 6. 查询所有教师
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/role/teacher

### 7. 统计人数
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/count

### 8. 分页查询（第1页，每页5条）
GET http://localhost:8081/api/test/page?page=0&size=5


### 9. 登录验证（admin）
POST http://localhost:8081/api/test/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 10. 登录验证（学生）
POST http://localhost:8081/api/test/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student001",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 11. 添加新用户
POST http://localhost:8081/api/test/add
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "test001",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "测试学生",
  "role": "student",
  "studentNo": "20240099",
  "className": "计算机3班",
  "phone": "13800123999",
  "email": "test@school.com",
  "status": 1
}

### 12. 更新用户
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/test/update/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "系统管理员",
  "role": "admin",
  "status": 1
}

### 13. 软删除用户
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/test/soft/10

### 14. 物理删除用户（慎用）
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/test/physical/10